@@TJvCustomValidateEdit.AsCurrency
Summary
Represents the Text property as a Currency value.

Description
Use AsCurrency to read the value of the Text property into an
\object or variable of type Currency or to assign a Currency
value to the Text property.



See Also
AsFloat, AsInteger, Text, Value

Note
If the current value of Text cannot be represented as a
currency value, AsCurrency returns 0.

@@TJvCustomValidateEdit.AsFloat
Summary
Represents the Text property as a Double value.

Description
Use AsFloat to read the value of the Text property into an
\object or variable of type Double or to assign a Double
value to the Text property.

Note
