@@TJvCustomValidateEdit.Assign
Summary
Copies the properties of another instance to this object.

Description
Use Assign to copy the properties of another
TJvCustomValidateEdit (or descendant) to this object. The
properties copied are CriticalPoints, DisplayFormat,
DecimalPlaces, MinValue, MaxValue, HasMinValue, HasMaxValue
and ZeroEmpty.



If Source is not derived from TJvCustomValidateEdit, Assign
calls inherited Assign.

Parameters
Source :  The object to copy from.
See Also

@@TJvCustomValidateEdit.AutoAlignment
Summary
Specifies if alignment is changed automatically.

Description
Use AutoAlignment to specify if the alignmnt of the text is
automatically changed when the DisplayFormat is changed. If
AutoAlignment is true, DisplayFormat's that are numeric in
nature are right-justified and all others are left-justified.
Set AutoAlignment to false to control the Alignment manually.

See Also
DisplayFormat, Alignment

